37:39.758 --> 37:41.589
Ah, you big lug.

37:41.593 --> 37:43.629
Ah, radu. Yes, master?

37:43.928 --> 37:46.419
Have you seen the mayor?
Yes, master. He's at breakfast.

37:46.431 --> 37:47.921
