37:47.932 --> 37:49.172
That's what you are.

37:49.184 --> 37:50.845
No, no, no, no. My name is Gil.

37:50.852 --> 37:52.433
Call me Gil.
I could not do that.

37:52.604 --> 37:54.390
Oh, sure you can.
