37:56.316 --> 37:57.351
Geh

37:58.943 --> 38:00.604
hello, Gil.

38:00.862 --> 38:01.897
Yes, Gil.

38:02.071 --> 38:04.027
Tha... that's fine.
Call me, call me master.

38:06.034 --> 38:07.365
Thank you, master.

38:10.789 --> 38:12.029
Ah, Mr. Turner.

38:14.751 --> 38:16.412
Good morning. - Good morning.

38:19.422 --> 38:20.422
Eqg?

38:20.548 --> 38:21.879
Cute. No, thank you.

38:22.550 --> 38:24.916
I sort of pack them in,
as you Americans say.

38:24.928 --> 38:26.338
They're standing in the aisles.

38:26.346 --> 38:28.632
Mayor, are we the only
guests in the hotel?

38:28.640 --> 38:30.551
Sure. Eh, this contractors.

38:30.809 --> 38:33.300
We don't open officially
yet for another month.

38:33.895 --> 38:34.895
