38:35.730 --> 38:36.719
I don't know.

38:36.731 --> 38:38.767
L... 1 thought I saw
someone in my room.

38:38.775 --> 38:39.981
I guess I was just dreaming.

38:39.984 --> 38:41.440
This castle can do it to you.

38:42.070 --> 38:43.901
First night I slept here...

38:44.656 --> 38:46.192
I thought I saw Dracula.

38:55.875 --> 38:57.331
That's funny.

38:57.335 --> 38:59.166
Are you and youru
partner having breakfast?

38:59.170 --> 39:00.250
No, he's still asleep.

39:00.255 --> 39:02.746
If you see him, tell him I'm going
into town to check on some things.

39:02.757 --> 39:04.122
Oh, yes, sure.

39:07.136 --> 39:08.171
Hey! - What?

39:08.179 --> 39:09.339
I want to show you something.

39:09.347 --> 39:11.133
Jeez, you scared
the hell out of me!

39:11.474 --> 39:12.964
Wait, wait, here. Here.
I got to get...

39:12.976 --> 39:14.682
No, no, wait! I don't have time.

39:14.686 --> 39:17.348
I want to show you.
Here, here, wait.

39:18.273 --> 39:19.308
See?

39:19.315 --> 39:20.315
Here.

39:22.110 --> 39:24.772
Oh, it's a beautiful day today.

39:25.613 --> 39:27.649
Hey, hey. Are you okay?

39:28.074 --> 39:30.406
What the hell? - No, I fine.

39:31.286 --> 39:32.286
You.

39:32.495 --> 39:34.110
I want you to try. Here.

39:34.706 --> 39:35.706
Here.

39:35.874 --> 39:37.614
No, no, no, no. I've got to go.
=you do it!

39:37.876 --> 39:39.491
Is good. Go, you be...
