39:40.336 --> 39:41.336
Hey!

39:42.505 --> 39:43.665
You can do it!

39:44.382 --> 39:45.382
Hey!

39:46.467 --> 39:47.798
Okay, we run!

40:29.552 --> 40:30.587
Radu.

40:30.970 --> 40:31.970
Yes, master.

40:32.597 --> 40:36.260
I want you to be sure no
one goes in the guest rooms.

40:36.267 --> 40:37.267
Yes, master.

41:13.888 --> 41:15.128
Hi. Yes?

41:15.139 --> 41:17.004
I'd like to see Dr. malavaqua.

41:17.266 --> 41:19.928
Only relatives of the
guest are allowed to visit.

41:20.228 --> 41:21.843
I can't even see the doctor?

41:22.355 --> 41:23.970
He only sees people
by appointment.

41:24.357 --> 41:26.268
Oh, okay, fine.
I'll make an appointment.

41:26.609 --> 41:29.146
He is not making
appointments at this time.

41:31.531 --> 41:32.566
I see.

41:33.866 --> 41:36.107
Ok, thank you for your help.

42:10.903 --> 42:11.903
Hi, ladies.

42:14.073 --> 42:15.404
Beautiful, isn't it?

42:19.579 --> 42:20.579
Have a nice day.

42:36.888 --> 42:38.298
Run! Run!

42:38.473 --> 42:39.588
I ook!

42:39.599 --> 42:41.806
It's Frankenstein!

42:42.018 --> 42:43.303
I don't like this.

42:45.188 --> 42:47.224
I don't like this at all.

42:48.733 --> 42:51.725
This film must be destroyed.

42:56.657 --> 42:58.898
Old age home... nothing!
All those disabled people.

42:58.910 --> 43:00.446
There's something going.
I don't know what.

43:00.453 --> 43:01.909
I don't know. Why all that security?

43:01.913 --> 43:04.370
I said okay, but when we see the
police, you do the talking.

43:04.373 --> 43:05.373
Hi

43:10.046 --> 43:13.504
I can well understand
your Frankenstein fixation.

43:13.508 --> 43:16.466
After all, you are
in transylvania.

43:16.636 --> 43:19.628
But in your own country...

43:20.098 --> 43:24.842
They still seek to write lurid
stories about your Jesse James

43:24.852 --> 43:26.012
or your dillinger.

43:26.020 --> 43:27.351
That was a long time ago.

43:27.355 --> 43:28.595
That is my point.

43:29.315 --> 43:33.979
The sinister image of transylvania
is our "long time ago."

43:34.278 --> 43:37.065
If you want to write about us,

43:37.073 --> 43:39.655
write about a happy transylvania.

43:39.867 --> 43:41.403
Our new sewer system.

43:41.410 --> 43:45.323
Our skyscraper...
Six floors, you know.

43:45.498 --> 43:48.490
Our newspaper didn't send us all
this way to write about a sewer.

43:49.085 --> 43:52.577
We can't have you
bothering Dr. malavaqua

43:52.588 --> 43:53.873
with your ludicrous questions.

43:54.340 --> 43:55.546
He's a busy man.

43:55.842 --> 43:58.549
Oh, really?
Is that why his license was revoked?

43:59.137 --> 44:00.137
Now, come on.

44:00.429 --> 44:02.294
This line of
inquiry is fruitless

44:02.306 --> 44:03.887
and beyond your concern.

44:03.891 --> 44:05.097
We must bid you a good day.

44:05.101 --> 44:06.716
What about all the people...
We're going now.

44:06.727 --> 44:08.513
What about them?
Thank you very much.

44:08.521 --> 44:09.852
Fine, fine.

44:09.856 --> 44:11.221
Goodbye. - Goodbye.

44:11.691 --> 44:14.808
And you are too serious.

44:14.819 --> 44:16.810
You must learn to frolic.

44:17.238 --> 44:19.229
Take up dance. Who knows?

44:19.240 --> 44:21.151
You could be another
Dean Astaire.

44:25.079 --> 44:28.071
Did you happen to catch the look on
their faces when I mentioned malavaqua?

44:28.082 --> 44:29.697
Okay, so they don't
want to talk about it.

44:29.709 --> 44:31.916
They're hiding something.
I don't believe that percek.

44:31.919 --> 44:34.001
All right. I got a few free hours.
Let's go.

44:34.005 --> 44:34.994
Where?

44:35.006 --> 44:37.167
To see that doctor and,
uh, get a second opinion.

44:37.175 --> 44:38.175
All right.

44:46.767 --> 44:47.802
Get down.

44:52.982 --> 44:53.982
Get up.

44:55.610 --> 44:56.610
Get down.

45:03.242 --> 45:04.242
Come on.

45:06.662 --> 45:07.662
Get up.

45:11.083 --> 45:12.803
The guard isn't there.
Why did you get down?

45:14.003 --> 45:15.914
I got into a rhythm.
What? Get up.

45:37.026 --> 45:38.311
Now, that's a coincidence.

45:38.653 --> 45:40.314
We just talked to percek and
the mayor about the doctor.

45:40.321 --> 45:41.481
Next thing we
know, they're here.

45:41.489 --> 45:43.104
I'd like to know what's
going on in there.

45:43.115 --> 45:44.605
Come on, maybe we can
get in through the back.

45:44.617 --> 45:45.617
Okay.

46:01.592 --> 46:03.173
What's this?
This is a chance to break in.

46:03.177 --> 46:04.417
You climb over this gate.

46:04.428 --> 46:05.463
One arm.

46:05.471 --> 46:07.007
If it's our chance,
why am I breaking in?

46:07.014 --> 46:09.734
You look more like a mental case.
Very funny. You know, I'm scared.

46:10.601 --> 46:12.307
What if this is electrified?
Here.

46:12.311 --> 46:14.431
There, see? It's not electrified.
Now, climb the gate.

46:14.605 --> 46:16.345
What if the guard sees me?
Just go.

46:16.565 --> 46:17.565
Okay, okay...

46:24.490 --> 46:27.072
Uh, patient trying to get out!
Patient trying to get out!

46:27.785 --> 46:28.905
What the hell are you doing?

46:29.453 --> 46:30.693
Hey, you!

46:33.708 --> 46:34.708
Please!

46:36.419 --> 46:37.784
Where do you think
you are going?

46:38.296 --> 46:39.296
Get back in there.

46:40.798 --> 46:41.833
You are new here?

46:42.591 --> 46:44.252
Didn't you get your
observation today?

46:45.219 --> 46:47.005
Later. Get back to work.

46:52.893 --> 46:56.602
Why this renewed concern
about my experimenting again?

46:57.023 --> 47:02.643
Two reporters have been inquiring
about, uh, Frankenstein monster.

47:04.780 --> 47:05.940
Frankenstein?

47:06.574 --> 47:07.905
That's ridiculous.

47:07.908 --> 47:08.908
Yes.

47:09.201 --> 47:11.157
That's what I told them.

47:12.872 --> 47:16.160
Your friend hunyadi
is the only one

47:16.167 --> 47:19.375
who might fit that
bizarre description.

47:19.378 --> 47:23.212
And you assured me
that he is deceased.

47:25.092 --> 47:28.129
May I see his file?

47:29.472 --> 47:31.884
Certainly, inspector percek.

47:32.892 --> 47:35.224
I filled out the death
certificate myself.

47:41.859 --> 47:45.727
And these others...
Patrick Glenn...

47:46.322 --> 47:48.529
Odette Barlow, John vlad.

47:50.117 --> 47:52.449
All dead as well? - Yes, sir.

47:52.661 --> 47:55.619
Ooh, you seem to be
in a roll, malavaqua.

47:57.583 --> 48:00.290
I enjoy these little visits.

48:01.170 --> 48:04.503
They relieve me of the
burdens my job can bring.

48:27.154 --> 48:29.566
Transylvania 6-5000.

48:29.865 --> 48:32.197
Fejos, could I
please speak to rad...

48:32.410 --> 48:34.366
Radu!

48:34.829 --> 48:37.912
Where are you? Here.

48:40.960 --> 48:42.075
Yes, master.

48:42.795 --> 48:45.161
Radu, are you alone?
Yes, master.

48:45.714 --> 48:46.794
Please, rad...

48:46.799 --> 48:49.757
Go to the laboratory and make
sure that hunyadi is there.

48:49.927 --> 48:51.212
He may be on the loose again.

48:51.220 --> 48:52.756
Yes, master. - Thank you

48:55.307 --> 48:58.094
Jack! I found out something.
How the hell do I get out of here?

48:58.102 --> 48:59.558
Simple. Go to the front
and climb over the wall.

48:59.562 --> 49:00.927
Take off the robe.
Are you crazy?

49:00.938 --> 49:02.394
The guard out front knows me.

49:03.357 --> 49:04.767
Trust me. - Uh, yeah.

49:04.775 --> 49:06.515
How come I always have
to do the trusting?

49:06.527 --> 49:08.188
Are you a middle child? - Yeah.

49:08.195 --> 49:09.195
So?

49:09.947 --> 49:10.947
Go!

49:23.043 --> 49:24.999
Man trying to get in!
Man trying to get in!

49:25.004 --> 49:26.665
Hey! Hey! You!

49:27.756 --> 49:28.836
It's you again!

49:29.049 --> 49:30.835
I told you before,
you couldn't come in.

49:31.218 --> 49:32.333
Now, get out!

49:36.474 --> 49:37.509
Stay out!

49:40.436 --> 49:42.552
That was brilliant.
But don't do that to me anymore.

49:42.563 --> 49:44.303
I'm anxiety prone.
Okay, did you get anything?

49:44.315 --> 49:45.896
Or did I waste my expertise
on dilly-dallying.

49:45.900 --> 49:48.767
Listen to this. Malavaqua called
that little weasel at the castle.

49:48.777 --> 49:50.392
Which weasel? = rad...

49:50.404 --> 49:52.269
He works for the doctor.
They're anxious to find hunyadi.

49:52.281 --> 49:54.522
And get this, they're
supposed to go to the lab.

49:54.533 --> 49:56.364
Who's hunyadi? And what lab?
=I don't know.

49:56.368 --> 49:57.858
But with all this
subterfuge and double talk,

49:57.870 --> 49:59.280
you got to admit
we're on to something.

49:59.288 --> 50:01.199
Maybe.
Maybe? I got a "maybe" out of you?

50:01.207 --> 50:02.947
Come on, let's go back to
the castle and see rad...

50:02.958 --> 50:04.698
Okay, you go.
And I'll meet you there later.

50:04.919 --> 50:05.919
Why aren't you going?

50:06.170 --> 50:07.205
I'm going to a picnic.

50:09.548 --> 50:10.548
Picnic?

50:28.108 --> 50:29.439
It's a lady doll.

50:31.278 --> 50:32.688
Just as I thought.

50:34.782 --> 50:37.114
Malavaqua has played
me for a fool.

50:41.956 --> 50:43.537
Put this in my car.

50:47.545 --> 50:48.580
Fvidence.

50:55.052 --> 50:57.168
I love you so much and everything.

50:57.179 --> 50:58.840
I wanted to help you because...

51:30.588 --> 51:33.125
Hi!

51:34.049 --> 51:35.880
Where is radu? =no.

51:35.884 --> 51:37.374
No radu. - No rad...

51:37.386 --> 51:39.377
Hey, you come in here.

51:39.388 --> 51:40.924
What are you doing in there?
= no, it's nice.

51:40.931 --> 51:42.371
Come in here.
