52:38.697 --> 52:41.217
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Have you been in my room at night?

52:41.617 --> 52:42.823
Did you want to hurt me?

52:43.369 --> 52:44.825
I do not.

52:45.204 --> 52:46.694
Bite you, yes.

52:46.705 --> 52:48.320
Wait a minute. Wait a minute...
I love you.

52:48.332 --> 52:50.368
Great, great, okay.
I want to kiss you.

52:50.376 --> 52:51.991
Can't we have lunch
first or something?

52:52.002 --> 52:54.118
Put your hands on my hips.
Okay...

52:54.713 --> 52:56.704
Put your arms around me.

52:57.466 --> 52:59.172
Put your face to my breast.

52:59.677 --> 53:01.258
Tell me you want me, too.

53:03.013 --> 53:05.220
Speak to me, baby. - I'm trying!

53:05.516 --> 53:08.428
Oh, I want you so bad, it hurts.

53:08.435 --> 53:09.595
You do?

53:10.604 --> 53:11.604
Oh, yeah.

53:13.148 --> 53:14.763
Oh, I like that.

53:15.526 --> 53:16.891
I want do to it some more.

53:18.612 --> 53:19.818
Oh, that hurt!

53:23.242 --> 53:24.322
Who is it?

53:26.120 --> 53:28.236
I better see who it is. Okay...

53:32.292 --> 53:33.532
Don't come in.

53:38.549 --> 53:40.085
Oh, come on now.

53:40.759 --> 53:41.874
Wait a minute.

53:45.139 --> 53:46.139
Aha.

53:49.768 --> 53:51.804
Hey! Is fast!

53:52.312 --> 53:53.677
What are you doing here?

53:53.689 --> 53:56.021
I'm meditating.
Did you see Dracula?

53:56.024 --> 53:57.935
Yah, yah. When it first came out.

53:57.943 --> 53:59.558
Not the movie! The person.

53:59.570 --> 54:01.106
Never mind. Never mind.
No, no, wait!

54:01.113 --> 54:02.694
Hey, I want to
show you something.

54:04.450 --> 54:06.657
Oh, my god! Are you okay? Look!

54:06.660 --> 54:07.866
Poor thing.

54:22.176 --> 54:23.176
Radu!

54:23.427 --> 54:24.712
Yes, master.

54:24.720 --> 54:27.211
Is hunyadi in the lab?
I have no time to check.

54:27.222 --> 54:28.632
I'm being followed, master.

54:28.974 --> 54:31.932
Radu, you're my friend
for 20 years. I love you.

54:31.935 --> 54:33.721
Please, don't call
me master anymore.

54:34.271 --> 54:35.727
Yes, ma... - That's good.

54:36.106 --> 54:37.106
Master.

54:38.984 --> 54:40.474
Well, maybe next time. Let's go.

54:54.041 --> 54:55.372
Thank you, radu.
You're very kind.

54:56.335 --> 54:58.291
You two are both
so helpful to me.

54:59.922 --> 55:02.789
Well, I'm all ready.

55:04.635 --> 55:05.875
Let's get to work.

55:29.952 --> 55:31.692
It's good to be home.

55:38.252 --> 55:39.537
My friends.

55:45.717 --> 55:47.503
Pompous percek.

55:48.387 --> 55:52.255
