just playing with white mice?

55:52.766 --> 55:54.302
Iitzy to fritzy, mitzy to fritzy!

55:54.810 --> 55:59.179
He thinks he can snuff
out the creative genius

55:59.189 --> 56:02.852
of the great victorio malavaqua?

56:03.235 --> 56:06.068
Mitzy, vitzy! Mitzy and vitzy.

56:06.071 --> 56:08.232
Shut up, you lowlife! =I'm low.

56:08.240 --> 56:10.652
