fun of my father.

56:17.833 --> 56:20.199
My father was a great scientist.

56:22.004 --> 56:24.586
He devoted his whole
life to try to cure

56:24.590 --> 56:27.548
the common cold by
injecting foreign viruses.

56:27.968 --> 56:30.084
And instead of being
honored for that...

56:31.054 --> 56:35.138
He's remembered as the man
who brought herpes to sicily.

56:37.603 --> 56:39.013
Don't worry, papa.

56:39.354 --> 56:42.812
My work will clear the
name of malavaqua forever!

56:44.902 --> 56:47.314
Hunyadi!

56:49.156 --> 56:51.522
Do not know.

56:51.533 --> 56:52.898
I don't know either!

56:52.910 --> 56:54.866
I tell you two to
keep an eye on them!

56:54.870 --> 56:57.031
