hell out of everybody!

56:57.414 --> 56:59.575
It's difficult working two jobs.

56:59.750 --> 57:00.865
Sure!

57:00.876 --> 57:04.414
It's more important to
feed those pigs upstairs!

57:04.838 --> 57:08.046
