57:14.765 --> 57:16.175
You hate it a lot, master.

57:16.183 --> 57:18.094
I hate it a lot, master.

57:18.101 --> 57:19.216
That's better. - Thank you.

57:19.227 --> 57:20.933
You're welcome.
You're welcome, what?

57:20.938 --> 57:23.304
You're welcome, master.
= shut up, you two!

57:23.482 --> 57:25.143
You matrimonial masochists!

57:25.317 --> 57:28.309
You found each other, but
you can't find anybody else!

57:31.823 --> 57:33.563
What are you laughing at?

57:33.575 --> 57:37.159
The joke is on you, you
stupid... get to work!

57:37.162 --> 57:38.743
This place is a mess! Clean up!

57:38.956 --> 57:40.537
Wash up! Clean up the floors!

57:40.540 --> 57:42.747
